{"tid":1915780,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗拿甸奴或被判監禁6個月！已被羈押不允許保釋","createTime":"2020-03-08T12:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T03:26:16.000Z","uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"86351b99015a2e997e2332c046846e56592aca23","tid":1915780,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:41:34.000Z","msg":"據《馬卡報》的最新消息，在當地時間週六，朗拿甸奴（Ronaldinho）和他的哥哥被送入了亞鬆森的看守所，此前法官下令將他們兩人羈押，並不允許被保釋。<br />\n  由於持假護照進入巴拉圭，朗拿甸奴和哥哥在本週被捕。因為拖欠環保罰款，朗拿甸奴的護照在2018年被巴西的司法機關沒收，這次他們去巴拉圭便偽造了假護照。<br />\n  當地地方法院法官路斯迪亞斯向法庭解釋了，為何在庭審結束後不加保釋，而直接將朗拿甸奴拘留的決定：「有充足的證據證明，朗拿甸奴使用了虛假的文件。」<br />\n  《馬卡報》表示，朗拿甸奴和他的哥哥可能會面臨長達6個月的監禁。法官路斯還解釋了為何不允許朗拿甸奴被保釋：「這樣一個非法進入本國的外國人，（被保釋後）有逃逸的風險。」<br />\n  （林登萬）"},{"pid":"0ac74d22b50dd06c9b1905a65487a831aae4f095","tid":1915780,"uid":173952,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6ba0gX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6ba0gX.jpg&h=819f1191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ov3s2vD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOv3s2vD.jpg&h=1e9da0cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f15b6450062583d06b4d19d9e1e488624aa0591","tid":1915780,"uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6MFC4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6MFC4D.jpg&h=5f9a946c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c362f707c4172a49d84769874cf5351e9c156605","tid":1915780,"uid":123848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"入到去有地道出番黎"},{"pid":"007ab369948c1719707f74c7c6edc9781cc3936f","tid":1915780,"uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0ac74d22b50dd06c9b1905a65487a831aae4f095","tid":1915780,"uid":173952,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img 